      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, offering an impeccable exterior and a cabin that remains in showroom state. Every mechanical component has been scrutinized to ensure peak performance, delivering an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such distinguished preservation.",
