    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s practically showroom fresh! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful 'new car' feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for with zero shortcuts taken, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
