      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I\u2019ve meticulously cared for it, keeping it garaged and pampered since day one. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior still has that fresh feel. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
