      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional E46 M3 that serves as a benchmark for naturally aspirated performance. The S54 straight-six engine is in peak mechanical health, breathing through individual throttle bodies and pulling cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a fully serviced double-VANOS system, addressing the critical weak points of the chassis. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The suspension maintains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the telepathic turn-in and lateral stability these cars are known for. A turn-key, investment-grade driver with no deferred maintenance.",
